data.description: ***ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AVAILABLE!! ***2.375%*** Welcome to your new contemporary home in the beautiful Rocky Ridge neighborhood. The home is situated toward the end of the road with very little traffic. Enjoy views of neighboring mountains to the east with gorgeous morning sunrises. Upon entering, you will notice the beautiful architecture and design. The living room boasts soaring ceilings, built in cabinetry, surround sound speakers, and a gas fireplace. The kitchen has hardwood floors, granite countertops, built in appliances and a walk-in pantry. There is a dining nook as well as a formal dining room. Two guest bedrooms are located on the north end of the home with one full bathroom. There is a bonus room above the garage, convenient for hobbies, or a rec room. The primary bedroom has an ensuite bathroom and large walk in closet, as well as access to the rear yard. In addition to the two-car attached garage, there is a 36x36 detached heated shop, fully insulated/finished. One door is 10' and the double door is 8'. Above the shop, is an ADU/apartment/mother-in-law suite which consists of 648 SF. It has a separate entrance and includes a studio apartment with full bathroom, kitchen, and laundry area. There is an electric chair lift for ease of access. Lots of concrete for clean living, and a beautiful level yard with privacy in the rear.
